data.description: Check out this fantastic opportunity to transform this split-level gem into your dream home! This property features 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and ample potential to make it your own. The home sits on a peaceful street giving it a family friendly atmosphere. Features new flooring throughout the house, large fenced in backyard, freshly painted siding and detached two car garage. Prime location near amenities such as the bike trail, park, library, elementary school nd Saylorville Lake. Great opportunity for a first-time homebuyer or an investor looking for significant potential for a profitable outcome.
